Package org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.packet

Class NASPortTypeAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.Attribute
      • org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.packet.NASPortTypeAttribute
  • public class NASPortTypeAttribute
extends Attribute
    Class representing the structure of the NAS-Port-Type field as specified in section 5.41 of RFC 2865 and able to be instantiated from the on-the-wire bytes or model objects.
